1934;;Beggars in Ermine;;American;;Phil Rosen;;Lionel Atwill, Jameson Thomas, Betty Furness;;drama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Beggars_in_Ermine;;John Dawson, a steel-mill owner loses his legs and his company in an accident engineered by his crooked secretary/treasurer, Jim Marley. After meeting a blind peddler, Marchant, he travels the country, under an assumed name, organizing beggars, peddlers, and the handicapped into a dues-paying system.